  <p class="pg-text">The HydraFacial™ treatment rejuvenates and protects your skin's health, providing immediate results without downtime.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">For those searching for a hydra facial near me in New Jersey, our medical-grade treatments address every skin type.</p>
