  <p class="pg-text">The exclusive three-step process cleanses, extracts, and hydrates with nourishing ingredients for an instantly gratifying glow, with minimal HydraFacial™ aftercare required.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">CLEANSE + PEEL</h3>
